text: Arest of horspoles heauede anlang dich on ludenham.
Of ludenhame alang streames on eldenham.
Þannen forð to þere ealden hege þannen forder be hegen one stoc wey.
Of stok wei anlang hecgham to filed hamme.
Of filed hamme ut þurth þere groue on irichte to þere eald dich.
Of here paþe anlang richtes to lortenwille on ða elden dich of þere ealden dic, on duccenhulle.
Of duccenhulle, on cawel andlang dich.
